<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{productName}} is Back in Stock - Goldmarks Jewellery</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">
        <h1 style="color: #d4af37; margin: 0;">Goldmarks Jewellery</h1>
        <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; color: #666;">Back in Stock Alert</p>
    </div>
    
    <div style="background: #d4edda; border: 1px solid #c3e6cb; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #155724; margin: 0; font-size: 24px;">Great News!</h2>
        <p style="color: #155724; margin: 10px 0 0 0;">The item you were waiting for is back!</p>
    </div>
    
    <div style="background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        {{{content}}}
    </div>
    
    {{#if limitedStock}}
    <div style="background: #f8d7da; border: 1px solid #f5c6cb; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center;">
        <p style="color: #721c24; margin: 0; font-weight: bold;">
            Limited Stock Alert: Only {{stockQuantity}} items remaining!
        </p>
    </div>
    {{/if}}
    
    <div style="background: #fff; border: 2px solid #d4af37; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
        <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #d4af37; text-align: center;">Why You'll Love This Item</h4>
        <ul style="color: #666; padding-left: 20px;">
            <li>Handcrafted with premium materials</li>
            <li>Exclusive Goldmarks design</li>
            <li>Perfect for special occasions</li>
            <li>Comes with authenticity certificate</li>
            <li>Free shipping on orders over $200</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 15px;">Don't miss out this time!</p>
        <a href="{{productUrl}}" style="background-color: #d4af37; color: white; padding: 15px 40px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; display: inline-block; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);">Buy Now - ${{productPrice}}</a>
    </div>
    
    <footer style="text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 14px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 20px;">
        <p>Best regards,<br><strong>The Goldmarks Jewellery Team</strong></p>
        <p style="margin-top: 20px;">
            <a href="#" style="color: #d4af37; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px;">View All Products</a> |
            <a href="#" style="color: #d4af37; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px;">Manage Notifications</a>
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #999; margin-top: 15px;">
            You're receiving this because you requested to be notified when this item was back in stock.
        </p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>